This method creates file handler with the localization. It's very helpful for translation static `.html`, `.txt` and `.md` files. Modern web applications are combined with many template files and this method solves problem with the localization. The method is linked with `F.onLocale()` delegate.

```javascript
// That's all
F.localize('/templates/*.html', ['minify']);

// Accept a new extension for the web server
F.accept('.hbs', 'text/html');
F.localize('/templates/*.hbs');
```

```html
http://127.0.0.1:8000/templates/settings.html --> will be localized
http://127.0.0.1:8000/templates/idontknow.html --> will be localized
http://127.0.0.1:8000/templates/ember.hbs --> will be localized
```

A custom mapping of static files. You can easily change a mapping static file. __IMPORTANT__: if you map some directory/file then the directory/file must exist otherwise the mapping won't be work.

### Mapping files

```javascript
// http://127.0.0.1:8000/app.js --> server responds with app-homepage.js script
F.map('/app.js', '/hidden-in-public-directory/app-homepage.js');
F.map('/app.js', F.path.private('/app-homepage.js'));
```

### Mapping directories

```javascript
// all files
F.map('/custom/', '/hidden-in-public-directory/');
F.map('/custom/', '~/hidden-in-root-directory/');

// only images
F.map('/custom/', F.path.root('my-images'), ['.png', '.gif', '.jpg']);

// custom filter
F.map('/custom/', F.path.private(), function(filename) {
    return filename.match(/\.(jpg|gif|png|js)$/i);
});
```

### Mapping for packages

```javascript
// all files
F.map('/custom/', '@package_name');

// only images
F.map('/custom/', '@package_name', ['.png', '.gif', '.jpg']);

// custom filter
F.map('/custom/', '@package_name', function(filename) {
    return filename.match(/\.(jpg|gif|png|js)$/i);
});
```

### Mapping for isomorphic code

```javascript
// below file is linked to /isomorphic/my-isomorphic.js
F.map('/serverside.js', '#my-isomorphic');
```

