    DATABASE('logs').insert({ message: 'I do not know.' }, self.error());
    self.json({ success: true });
}
```

Returns the wrapped function `callback(err, some_data)`. In case of the error the framework throws `controller.throw500(error)` and if the error is `ErrorBuilder` then the framework responds with `controller.content(error)`.

```javascript
// Returns the JSON
framework.database('some_db').all(controller.callback());

// Returns the "my-view" view
framework.database('some_db').all(controller.callback('my-view'))
```

