api.body:
The __TransformBuilder__ is very helpful for transformation plain objects.

- TransformBuilder is a global object

### Creating transformation

```javascript
TransformBuilder.addTransform('xml', function(obj) {
    var builder = '';
    Object.keys(obj).forEach(function(key) {
        var value = obj[key];
        if (value === undefined || value === null)
            value = '';
        builder += '<' + key + '>' + value.toString().encode() + '</' + key + '>';
    });
    return '<xml>' + builder + '</xml>';
});
```

### Applying transformation

```javascript
var user = { name: 'Peter Širka', email: 'petersirka@gmail.com' };
console.log(TransformBuilder.transform('xml', user));
// OUTPUT: <xml><name>Peter Širka</name><email>petersirka@gmail.com</email></xml>
```

