module#monitor      (Object)   : { url: '/mymonitor/' }
module#webcounter   (Object)   : { xhr: true, ip: true }
```

__Usage in own modules:__

```javascript
exports.install = function(options) {
    // options === CUSTOM OPTIONS
};
```

